msgid "Update Python-Qt key map to include PageUp and PageDown"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/python-qt-missing-keys.md:3
msgid ""
"The QVTKRenderWindowInteractor now maps the `PageUp` and `PageDown` keys to "
"their corresponding VTK keysyms \"Prior\" and \"Next\".  Previously, the Qt-"
"to-keysym mappings for these keys were only available through C++."
